{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC19"]]},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"overridingTitle":"Watch Video (40 min)","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc19\/416","type":"reference"}},"kind":"article","primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"XCFramework","level":2,"text":"XCFramework"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A XCFramework is multiple binary frameworks in one package.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can bundle:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"a variant of the framework for each target (iPhones, Simulators)."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"a variant of the same framework for different platforms:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"WWDC19-416-platform","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"We can also have variants with different dependencies as well:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"WWDC19-416-dep","type":"image"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"XCFrameworks support both Swift and “c-based” code.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"How-do-XCFrameworks-work","level":2,"text":"How do XCFrameworks work?"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Like another binary, but the header is a new Swift Module Interfaces type, which, kind of like the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Package.swift"},{"type":"text","text":" file for SPM packages, contains information on the required compiler version and a full list of public classes and methods available from within the framework."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"How-to-create-a-XCFrameworks","level":2,"text":"How to create a XCFrameworks"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We have a new setting:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC19-416-build"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In order to release a binary we need to archive the framework (a.k.a. build in release mode) and the output will be available in the organizer."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default path is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\/Users\/YOURUSERNAME\/Library\/Developer\/Xcode\/Archives"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"￼"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"We can change the output path in Xcode Locations from the preferences window.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After archiving different frameworks we can create a final "},{"code":".xcframework","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" by using the command line:"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"syntax":"shell","code":["xcodebuild-create-xcframework ","  -framework [path] ","  -framework [path] ","  ...","  -framework [path] ","  -output FlightKit.xcframework "],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Written-By","level":2,"text":"Written By"},{"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"zntfdr","type":"image"}]}]},{"size":4,"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Federico-Zanetello","text":"Federico Zanetello","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Contributed Notes","type":"reference","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Contributed Notes"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/zntfdr"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"|","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":